[SN]TITLE[SN]
Guide dog owner warns of dangers of pavement parking

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A guide dog owner has warned of the dangers of pavement parking, as a campaign is launched to urge NI drivers to consider the needs of those with disabilities.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 February 2017 Last updated at 16:10 GMT
The PSNI has revealed it will be issuing notices to badly parked cars.
Diane Marks explained the safety issues that pavement parking can cause.
